# MEMORY.md — Long-Term Agent Memory
# Curated facts only. Never write here directly during tasks.
# Updated by the consolidation program.
# Target: ≤ 200 lines. Hard cap: 400 lines.
#
# Structure: Six-Vector Memory
# Facts are organised into 6 retrieval vectors so agents can read the right
# section intelligently rather than scanning everything.
# See references/RETRIEVAL.md for how to use this file at query time.

---

